WEBVTT

00:06.981 --> 00:09.920
(Opera. The Life of Luo Shan)

00:09.921 --> 00:12.421
Sir, it's a new play titled,
"The Life of Luo Shan."

00:12.431 --> 00:14.840
It's about a motherless child
who brings his father to court.

00:14.841 --> 00:17.141
A life of drifting
with emotional entanglement.

00:17.161 --> 00:18.670
A father and son relationship
that is hard to sever.

00:18.671 --> 00:19.811
Please, come inside.

00:22.861 --> 00:26.881
(Opera. The Life of Luo Shan)

00:32.921 --> 00:34.181
Please head inside.

00:39.801 --> 00:41.411
Keep a close watch

00:41.601 --> 00:42.861
on the woman with the fox mask.

00:42.871 --> 00:43.780
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:43.781 --> 00:47.181
So, how does the story unfold?

00:48.111 --> 00:50.051
The entire family

00:50.071 --> 00:55.221
was killed by the bandit, Xu Neng.

00:56.161 --> 00:58.181
Xu Neng

00:59.031 --> 01:02.371
is my father's name.

01:02.521 --> 01:05.101
Could my father really...?

01:06.111 --> 01:11.821
Outrageous!

01:12.671 --> 01:15.261
Good!

01:16.161 --> 01:17.301
The play is excellent.

01:18.601 --> 01:21.661
But sadly, the son discovers
that his father is not only a bandit

01:21.671 --> 01:23.491
but might also be the one
who killed his mother.

01:23.751 --> 01:25.771
It seems like this is a tragedy.

01:25.771 --> 01:27.361
Sir, please enjoy
and see how it unfolds.

01:31.671 --> 01:33.101
But not necessarily.

01:33.671 --> 01:35.101
People love to watch plays

01:35.361 --> 01:36.851
because they always end the play

01:37.311 --> 01:38.640
with a reunion

01:38.641 --> 01:40.331
no matter how deep the grudges.

01:40.551 --> 01:43.901
Life, on the other hand,
is harder than that.

01:45.881 --> 01:48.611
Happiness finds company,
sorrow finds none.

01:48.881 --> 01:50.181
If you don't believe it,

01:50.721 --> 01:52.131
why not watch and see

01:52.551 --> 01:54.691
if the ending is tragic or joyful?

01:55.271 --> 01:56.411
Sure.

01:56.721 --> 01:59.440
With the screen removed and accompanied
by the candlelight and gentle breeze,

01:59.441 --> 02:00.661
it will be much more spacious.

02:01.671 --> 02:02.520
Waiter!

02:02.521 --> 02:03.640
Remove this screen.

02:03.641 --> 02:04.781
I'll move it right away.

02:17.461 --> 02:21.240
(Exquisite Melodies)

02:21.241 --> 02:24.360
Wonderful!

02:24.361 --> 02:25.430
How strange.

02:25.431 --> 02:27.541
It's neither a tragedy
nor a happy ending.

02:27.761 --> 02:29.221
Is the play unfinished?

02:29.321 --> 02:31.821
The son is an official,
and the father is a bandit.

02:32.361 --> 02:34.131
Family and justice

02:34.151 --> 02:36.291
become two uncompromising sides.

02:36.541 --> 02:38.061
The ending is naturally hard to write.

02:38.521 --> 02:39.710
If the second half showed

02:39.711 --> 02:41.661
a son trying his father in court,

02:42.391 --> 02:43.971
wouldn't that be shocking?

02:44.551 --> 02:47.691
Do you think
a son shouldn't try his father?

02:47.991 --> 02:50.061
Should family always come
before justice?

02:51.151 --> 02:52.430
I meant

02:52.431 --> 02:55.131
there's nothing wrong
with shocking the world.

02:55.401 --> 02:57.080
Filial piety may be the greatest virtue.

02:57.081 --> 02:58.641
But loyalty to the country comes first
when you're an official.

02:58.641 --> 02:59.830
The question

02:59.831 --> 03:01.760
is whether he wants to be a good son

03:01.761 --> 03:03.451
or a good official.

03:04.241 --> 03:05.941
There's no way to be both.

03:06.391 --> 03:09.291
Whichever way he chooses,
it's bound to end in tragedy.

03:10.961 --> 03:14.011
The main character is a tragic figure.

03:15.151 --> 03:18.131
(I think he is heartbroken)

03:18.161 --> 03:20.061
(because he is also struggling
between family and justice.)

03:24.481 --> 03:26.291
How would you write it?

03:28.271 --> 03:31.171
In court, try the cases as you should.

03:32.241 --> 03:35.691
At home, you're a son again.

03:35.991 --> 03:37.891
Put aside all the talk of big principles

03:38.711 --> 03:40.661
and just softly coax him.

03:40.671 --> 03:41.851
If that doesn't work,

03:42.041 --> 03:43.851
you can just kneel on a washboard.

03:46.241 --> 03:47.941
That would turn it into a comedy, then.

03:50.991 --> 03:52.661
Dear audience, you are in luck!

03:52.671 --> 03:54.291
To celebrate the festive season,

03:54.391 --> 03:55.960
I've prepared

03:55.961 --> 03:58.920
a guessing game and a little gift

03:58.921 --> 04:01.261
to entertain you all.

05:22.141 --> 05:24.430
=Blossom=

05:24.431 --> 05:26.340
(Adapted from the novel
"Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

05:26.341 --> 05:29.561
=Episode 4=

05:29.641 --> 05:32.331
All the items used in the game are
from the tavern.

05:33.351 --> 05:35.861
The performers' acts
will serve as hints.

05:36.081 --> 05:38.350
Everyone here can guess.

05:38.351 --> 05:40.181
The one with the most correct answers
wins.

05:42.881 --> 05:45.301
Let's begin with the first question.

05:46.521 --> 05:50.520
In the city, the battle horses roam.

05:50.521 --> 05:55.571
Each year, the land is filled
with corpses and crows' cries.

05:56.271 --> 05:57.411
Battle horses?

05:58.561 --> 06:00.131
That is too small for them.

06:00.441 --> 06:01.760
It's "The Blossom."

06:01.761 --> 06:04.181
Ni Heng beats the drum
and insults Cao Cao.

06:04.831 --> 06:06.181
It's a drumstick.

06:06.911 --> 06:08.051
Correct!

06:08.201 --> 06:09.381
Great answer!

06:12.881 --> 06:15.451
I'm surprised you know
about historical weapons.

06:16.031 --> 06:18.691
Could you be a man dressing as a woman?

06:20.561 --> 06:22.211
Well, women can be as capable as men.

06:29.711 --> 06:31.451
Let's move to the second question.

06:31.591 --> 06:34.760
These are hairpins and skirts,

06:34.761 --> 06:36.960
standing tall to hold up the sky.

06:36.961 --> 06:41.381
What's this talk of a man's role?

06:41.961 --> 06:44.061
Hua Mulan joined the army
in place of her father.

06:44.151 --> 06:46.621
She removed her makeup
and disguised herself as a man.

06:46.881 --> 06:50.571
The object in the box is a rouge used
by female performers.

06:51.441 --> 06:52.581
Correct!

06:53.321 --> 06:54.461
Impressive!

06:55.591 --> 06:57.981
You seem quite familiar
with women's products.

06:58.321 --> 07:00.331
Could it be you often frequent
such places?

07:00.881 --> 07:02.861
In books,
there are beauties like Yan Ruyu.

07:13.081 --> 07:15.320
If I must say, why don't you two
go home and compete?

07:15.321 --> 07:16.590
It's meaningless to argue here.

07:16.591 --> 07:17.960
- Don't you all agree?
- Leave now.

07:17.961 --> 07:19.621
- That's right.
- Go home.

07:19.711 --> 07:20.891
That would be boring.

07:21.471 --> 07:22.981
Competing is the fun part.

07:23.151 --> 07:24.000
That's right.

07:24.001 --> 07:25.200
If I just admit defeat,

07:25.201 --> 07:27.211
it's not worth being a man at all.

07:29.711 --> 07:31.771
Is there a third question?

07:31.831 --> 07:33.011
That's right.

07:33.201 --> 07:34.741
Is there a third riddle?

07:35.681 --> 07:37.520
Here comes the third riddle.

07:37.521 --> 07:41.350
The song of Chu brings sorrow

07:41.351 --> 07:45.560
with tears filling the eyes.

07:45.561 --> 07:47.760
The Battle of Gaixia,
surrounded by Chu's soldiers.

07:47.761 --> 07:49.531
- The Chu army missed home.
- The Chu army...

07:50.521 --> 07:52.771
Those who miss home want
to return home.

07:54.791 --> 07:57.011
The item is Angelica Root,

07:57.201 --> 07:58.341
a dish in the tavern.

08:11.441 --> 08:12.320
Correct!

08:12.321 --> 08:13.560
Excellent!

08:13.561 --> 08:15.960
Miss, you won this round.

08:15.961 --> 08:17.520
We both answered together.

08:17.521 --> 08:18.821
But I was quicker.

08:19.271 --> 08:20.411
Thank you for yielding.

08:20.681 --> 08:22.691
The words you spoke so easily

08:23.081 --> 08:24.941
were a luxury I could not even dream of.

08:25.591 --> 08:26.891
I admit my defeat.

08:37.471 --> 08:39.861
What do you think
this person is thinking?

08:40.751 --> 08:42.381
He's upset
and does not accept his defeat.

08:45.831 --> 08:49.051
He's thinking about his family

08:49.201 --> 08:51.771
and the hometown
he hasn't returned to for a long time.

08:54.801 --> 08:55.941
Congratulations, miss.

08:57.401 --> 08:58.541
Thank you.

09:03.041 --> 09:04.651
Twenty-Four Stories of Filial Piety.

09:05.591 --> 09:06.731
It's a pity

09:07.081 --> 09:08.411
I can no longer use this.

09:20.231 --> 09:21.371
Mister!

09:22.591 --> 09:23.731
Mister,

09:25.471 --> 09:27.101
Young Lady sent me to give you this.

09:35.921 --> 09:38.411
(Allow me to be bold enough
to guess what's on your mind.)

09:38.801 --> 09:40.131
(I wonder if I am right.)

09:40.991 --> 09:42.651
(You are well-versed in knowledge)

09:43.041 --> 09:44.501
(with unmatched talents.)

09:44.501 --> 09:46.081
(But you're defeated
by family problems.)

09:46.751 --> 09:48.221
(If your family is still around,)

09:48.751 --> 09:50.411
(why not compromise and give it a try?)

09:50.751 --> 09:52.861
(Like doing something
that brings joy to your parents.)

09:54.041 --> 09:56.541
♪I rise on tiptoes♪

09:56.901 --> 09:58.890
♪To kiss your brow♪

09:58.891 --> 10:04.381
♪From now on,
my heart needs no disguise♪

10:04.851 --> 10:07.181
♪Wrapped in frost and snow♪

10:07.201 --> 10:10.221
(Behind the mask and the role play,)

10:10.871 --> 10:13.011
(she is surprisingly insightful
and sharp.)

10:14.751 --> 10:18.710
♪I hold onto this love
for the world to see♪

10:18.711 --> 10:21.301
Your Lordship, the Marshal
urgently requests your return.

10:21.401 --> 10:22.710
The storm is approaching Futing

10:22.711 --> 10:24.331
and we need to return and provide help.

10:29.441 --> 10:30.861
A fragrance ball?

10:41.041 --> 10:42.341
It's a woman's item.

10:42.831 --> 10:44.381
Did Your Lordship just...

10:44.711 --> 10:45.830
Don't make any wild guesses.

10:45.831 --> 10:47.151
I was at the theater to watch a play.

10:48.081 --> 10:50.891
It might have gotten caught
when I was passing by other audiences.

10:51.321 --> 10:53.931
You left the army quietly this time.

10:54.161 --> 10:55.831
So it's best not to expose
your whereabouts.

10:55.831 --> 10:57.131
You should discard it.

10:59.081 --> 11:00.341
If a woman's personal belongings

11:00.471 --> 11:02.581
fall into the wrong hands,
won't that cause trouble?

11:03.321 --> 11:06.341
I will return it to her
if I see her again.

11:06.751 --> 11:07.680
By the way,

11:07.681 --> 11:10.741
deliver this lantern to my father.

11:15.871 --> 11:17.861
Let's meet at the post station
in an hour.

11:22.181 --> 11:24.891
Scented sachets, charms,
and little trinkets for sale!

11:25.071 --> 11:27.701
Sugar-coated hawthorn for sale!

11:48.161 --> 11:50.320
Once I finish my business at dawn,
I'll bring her back.

11:50.321 --> 11:52.510
You all should leave
and lay low for now.

11:52.511 --> 11:54.171
- Yes.
- Leave now.

12:05.161 --> 12:06.301
Pang Kunbai?

12:07.961 --> 12:08.990
What are you trying to do?

12:08.991 --> 12:10.131
What do you think?

12:10.591 --> 12:12.981
I'm obviously going
to show you some affection.

12:17.041 --> 12:18.181
How did you...

12:23.871 --> 12:24.780
All... All of you...

12:24.781 --> 12:25.630
Let me enjoy

12:25.631 --> 12:27.261
your affection, then.

12:27.281 --> 12:28.421
Get him!

12:29.041 --> 12:30.181
Stop it.

12:30.871 --> 12:32.011
Stop hitting me.

12:32.511 --> 12:33.651
Spare me!

12:35.241 --> 12:37.811
Who knew stargazing would lead
to such a drama.

12:38.471 --> 12:39.621
Interesting, indeed.

12:41.751 --> 12:43.051
Miss, spare us.

12:43.111 --> 12:44.710
We were only doing our part
for the money.

12:44.711 --> 12:47.111
You use your skills to bully women
and ruin their reputations

12:47.111 --> 12:49.741
instead of putting your skills
to good use.

12:49.991 --> 12:51.411
Killing you wouldn't be unjust.

12:56.031 --> 12:57.830
Fourth Young Lady Dou,
it's all a misunderstanding.

12:57.831 --> 12:59.990
Those scoundrels knocked me out
and brought me here!

12:59.991 --> 13:01.701
I don't know anything.

13:01.751 --> 13:03.510
Stop! I'll take responsibility for you!

13:03.511 --> 13:04.990
I'll marry you
with all the proper ceremonies

13:04.991 --> 13:06.320
and make sure no one criticizes you.

13:06.321 --> 13:07.350
Just keep your mouth shut.

13:07.351 --> 13:08.200
At the family banquet,

13:08.201 --> 13:10.040
I saw you exchanged looks
with Wang Yingxue.

13:10.041 --> 13:12.381
I knew it wasn't a simple banquet.

13:12.411 --> 13:14.111
So I sent someone
to investigate your background.

13:14.111 --> 13:16.381
You're a nephew of the Wang Family.

13:16.441 --> 13:18.230
You're scheming on using nonsense

13:18.231 --> 13:19.981
about what gossip can do
to one's reputation.

13:20.201 --> 13:22.131
Did you think
Young Lady would suffer in silence?

13:22.131 --> 13:23.960
You're coveting her hard-earned savings
from over ten years

13:23.961 --> 13:24.820
to become part of her dowry

13:24.821 --> 13:26.341
so it can fill your family's pockets!

13:26.411 --> 13:28.891
I want to see what happens
when this matter reaches the court.

13:29.561 --> 13:31.131
Is it me afraid
of being schemed against,

13:31.321 --> 13:33.910
or your Wang Family afraid
of having your reputation ruined?

13:33.911 --> 13:35.051
Take him away.

13:43.871 --> 13:45.011
Get lost.

13:51.561 --> 13:52.701
Little Zhuang Zhou,

13:52.711 --> 13:55.381
it seems
Grandmother has taken good care of you.

13:55.591 --> 13:57.931
This was a storybook left behind
by a carefree hermit.

13:58.041 --> 13:59.701
He said it's for someone with fate.

14:00.161 --> 14:01.000
It seems

14:01.001 --> 14:02.891
you're that Little Zhuang Zhou he meant.

14:04.961 --> 14:06.101
Yuantong?

14:08.321 --> 14:09.461
Is it really you?

14:10.111 --> 14:11.350
Why are you here?

14:11.351 --> 14:12.811
Since you're one of us,

14:12.921 --> 14:14.861
why did you let Pang Kunbai go?

14:17.561 --> 14:18.931
Are you putting an act for me?

14:22.591 --> 14:23.731
Aunt!

14:23.961 --> 14:25.101
Aunt!

14:26.761 --> 14:27.710
Look at you.

14:27.711 --> 14:29.870
Aunt, we're done for.

14:29.871 --> 14:32.261
What happened to you?

14:33.041 --> 14:35.510
You're a grown man helped
by a group of people.

14:35.511 --> 14:37.741
How did a young girl put you
in such a sorry state?

14:37.871 --> 14:38.800
Aunt,

14:38.801 --> 14:40.510
she was already prepared for this.

14:40.511 --> 14:42.051
We have been played.

14:42.111 --> 14:43.501
You're so useless.

14:43.711 --> 14:45.590
Madam! Madam, we have trouble.

14:45.591 --> 14:47.341
Fourth Young Lady has arrived
with the guards.

14:49.631 --> 14:50.830
Head to the side room quickly.

14:50.831 --> 14:52.621
Go and hide there now.

14:57.681 --> 14:58.821
Madam,

14:59.231 --> 15:00.621
is everything all right here?

15:00.681 --> 15:03.131
I was robbed while I was enjoying
the Lantern Festival.

15:03.201 --> 15:05.990
I even followed Officer Wang
from the yamen to chase him all the way here.

15:05.991 --> 15:08.811
But I realized that this is our house.

15:09.351 --> 15:11.051
This is the Dou's Residence, you know.

15:11.081 --> 15:12.811
The outlaws wouldn't dare to enter.

15:12.831 --> 15:14.261
What nonsense.

15:14.801 --> 15:15.720
Let me go!

15:15.721 --> 15:16.891
- Let me go!
- Officer Wang,

15:17.111 --> 15:18.230
he is right here.

15:18.231 --> 15:19.371
You...

15:20.511 --> 15:21.590
How dare you.

15:21.591 --> 15:23.811
These two are from the same household.

15:24.161 --> 15:26.291
Who's this troublemaker barking here?

15:27.161 --> 15:28.651
Greetings, Madam Wang.

15:29.201 --> 15:30.320
My name is Ji Yong,

15:30.321 --> 15:32.291
a distant relative of Old Madam Cui.

15:32.511 --> 15:33.680
I lodged the report.

15:33.681 --> 15:35.701
Mr. Ji is the top scholar
in the provincial exam.

15:35.751 --> 15:36.931
Arrest him!

15:38.561 --> 15:39.701
Let me go!

15:39.801 --> 15:41.411
Aunt! Aunt!

15:41.631 --> 15:42.981
Aunt, help me!

15:42.991 --> 15:44.350
Aunt!

15:44.351 --> 15:45.491
Madam,

15:46.711 --> 15:48.651
betrayal from one's family truly hurts.

15:49.631 --> 15:52.221
He even said this was your idea.

15:52.511 --> 15:53.651
You...

15:53.681 --> 15:55.680
This is a serious matter.

15:55.681 --> 15:57.440
I'll go and get Fifth Master
and Seventh Master

15:57.441 --> 15:58.981
to go to the government office together.

15:58.991 --> 16:01.341
We can sort out
any misunderstandings there.

16:03.321 --> 16:04.891
No! This is...

16:05.041 --> 16:07.531
Fifth Master and Seventh Master
are already asleep.

16:08.041 --> 16:10.051
Let's not trouble the both of them.

16:11.891 --> 16:13.221
Your acting was very convincing.

16:14.211 --> 16:16.201
If you went straight
to report this to the authorities,

16:16.201 --> 16:19.080
they wouldn't dare act

16:19.081 --> 16:20.421
against the Wang Family
or the Dou Family's influence.

16:20.891 --> 16:22.901
But catching them red-handed
is a different matter.

16:23.511 --> 16:24.710
Wang Yingxue will have

16:24.711 --> 16:26.291
a hard time explaining this to Father

16:26.711 --> 16:28.171
and the Wang Family.

16:29.511 --> 16:30.360
Absurd!

16:30.361 --> 16:31.981
Absolutely ridiculous!

16:32.351 --> 16:34.381
He's only a distant nephew.

16:34.591 --> 16:36.990
You'd rather believe him than me?

16:36.991 --> 16:38.730
Kidnapping is such a serious crime.

16:38.731 --> 16:40.791
How dare he falsely accuse me of it?

16:40.871 --> 16:42.940
Your own nephew turned around
and accused you.

16:42.941 --> 16:44.261
How could that be fake?

16:44.391 --> 16:46.381
I just don't understand.

16:46.441 --> 16:49.291
You used to be kind and patient.

16:49.661 --> 16:51.741
What happened to you?

16:54.641 --> 16:55.781
My dear,

16:56.801 --> 16:59.741
is it me who's changed, or is it you?

17:00.921 --> 17:04.261
No matter how others mocked me before,

17:04.711 --> 17:07.371
you would always love and protect me.

17:07.511 --> 17:09.771
But somewhere along the way,

17:10.751 --> 17:15.051
our relationship was no longer the same.

17:15.681 --> 17:18.011
We become a married couple in the name.

17:18.511 --> 17:20.181
Ever since we sleep in separate rooms,

17:20.401 --> 17:22.661
you've decided that I'm the bad person.

17:22.881 --> 17:25.960
You would blame me

17:25.961 --> 17:28.051
whenever anything bad happens
to Dou Zhao.

17:31.991 --> 17:32.990
I'm just stating facts.

17:32.991 --> 17:34.391
Stop bringing up unrelated matters.

17:35.011 --> 17:36.661
It's not unrelated.

17:37.071 --> 17:39.440
I know you can't let go
of Guqiu's death.

17:39.441 --> 17:42.291
So you let me take that fall!

17:42.471 --> 17:43.901
Sixteen years have passed.

17:44.481 --> 17:46.531
Has Dou Zhao ever fulfilled
her duties as a daughter?

17:47.231 --> 17:49.011
But as for me,

17:49.751 --> 17:52.661
I've given everything I have
to the Dou Family,

17:52.841 --> 17:55.531
both at home and in the court.

17:55.991 --> 17:57.960
What else do you want from me?

17:57.961 --> 17:59.941
Why don't you just divorce me already?

18:00.711 --> 18:02.531
Yingxue. Yingxue!

18:02.681 --> 18:04.070
That's not what I meant.

18:04.071 --> 18:06.230
But Ms. Longevity did suffer
from the incident.

18:06.231 --> 18:07.371
Father.

18:08.361 --> 18:09.501
Mother.

18:12.361 --> 18:13.680
Zhao has prepared a carriage

18:13.681 --> 18:15.141
and is ready to leave soon.

18:16.441 --> 18:17.581
Ming,

18:18.121 --> 18:20.941
your mother's eyes are irritated
by pollen.

18:20.961 --> 18:22.531
Help her wipe them.

18:23.681 --> 18:24.821
Yes, Father.

18:31.511 --> 18:32.981
You devoted yourself to this family.

18:33.401 --> 18:35.051
Father knows that.

18:35.161 --> 18:36.301
I know.

18:36.991 --> 18:39.291
But he still favors Dou Zhao.

18:39.471 --> 18:41.531
If I didn't make a scene just now,

18:41.641 --> 18:43.941
how else could I remove the thorn?

18:44.231 --> 18:46.221
Father wants harmony in the family.

18:46.921 --> 18:48.461
Why not show some generosity

18:48.471 --> 18:50.920
and make peace
with Zhao and Grandmother?

18:50.921 --> 18:52.571
I'm the matron of this house!

18:53.121 --> 18:54.701
Why should I humble myself to them?

18:54.991 --> 18:56.501
Are you out of your mind?

18:57.441 --> 18:58.771
As long as she stays unmarried,

18:59.161 --> 19:00.811
you can't discuss your marriage.

19:00.921 --> 19:02.771
Her wealth

19:03.071 --> 19:05.421
should be part of your dowry.

19:05.641 --> 19:07.440
I don't care

19:07.441 --> 19:09.261
about the amount of my dowry

19:09.361 --> 19:10.880
or when my wedding happens.

19:10.881 --> 19:12.221
You fool!

19:14.161 --> 19:18.901
I've never given the Dou Family a son.

19:19.601 --> 19:21.571
So I'm forced to play the bad person

19:22.161 --> 19:23.941
and fight for everything.

19:24.161 --> 19:25.941
But I never imagined

19:25.991 --> 19:28.291
you grew up to be such
a spineless child.

19:28.841 --> 19:30.160
I don't even know why

19:30.161 --> 19:31.661
I've been fighting all this time.

19:32.681 --> 19:34.091
If I'd known this,

19:34.471 --> 19:36.160
I would never have

19:36.161 --> 19:38.181
let someone else raise you.

19:39.471 --> 19:40.611
Mother,

19:41.201 --> 19:42.600
I know I've let you down.

19:42.601 --> 19:44.200
But I don't want you

19:44.201 --> 19:46.371
to risk so much for my sake.

19:47.861 --> 19:50.200
Lending money at interest
is strictly forbidden by the court.

19:50.201 --> 19:51.230
All these years,

19:51.231 --> 19:53.310
you've been dealing
with the cutthroat Cangbei Gang...

19:53.311 --> 19:54.451
Quiet!

19:54.881 --> 19:55.920
How dare you speak

19:55.921 --> 19:57.571
of such things?

20:00.031 --> 20:01.261
Cry?

20:01.361 --> 20:02.470
Is crying all you know?

20:02.471 --> 20:03.851
Crying is useless.

20:03.881 --> 20:05.221
I know.

20:05.511 --> 20:07.941
But I can't control my tears.

20:08.471 --> 20:10.091
I'm useless.

20:13.751 --> 20:14.891
Ming,

20:14.921 --> 20:16.771
you must listen to everything I say

20:16.841 --> 20:18.771
since you admit crying is useless.

20:19.711 --> 20:20.901
Remember this.

20:21.031 --> 20:24.421
Your dowry, family background,
and reputation

20:24.611 --> 20:26.501
all affect your future marriage.

20:27.401 --> 20:29.221
If I don't fight for it,

20:29.441 --> 20:30.550
you'll live

20:30.551 --> 20:33.011
in constant fear and uncertainty
in the future.

20:34.311 --> 20:36.501
You can't even control your emotions.

20:36.881 --> 20:39.470
Let alone the hardships
of being a wife.

20:39.471 --> 20:41.371
How can you endure all that?

20:45.161 --> 20:46.301
Ms. Longevity.

20:49.031 --> 20:50.171
Ms. Longevity,

20:50.361 --> 20:52.051
I failed to protect you.

20:52.511 --> 20:54.291
It is all my fault.

20:54.751 --> 20:56.811
I will definitely make it up to you.

20:57.161 --> 20:58.571
It's not your fault, Father.

20:59.791 --> 21:02.051
I should never have expected anything
in the first place.

22:02.071 --> 22:03.211
All done.

22:03.441 --> 22:05.741
Peony fillet, a famous Sichuan dish.

22:05.751 --> 22:08.181
This Peony fillet
is so complicated to make

22:08.201 --> 22:10.120
It's hard to find something like this
in the restaurants of the capital.

22:10.121 --> 22:11.860
Ms. Longevity,
who taught you how to make it?

22:13.511 --> 22:14.741
Then I'll try a bite first.

22:14.841 --> 22:15.981
Zhangru,

22:16.121 --> 22:17.771
I made this for Ji Jianming.

22:17.961 --> 22:19.811
It's not proper if you eat it first.

22:20.311 --> 22:21.531
Fine.

22:21.601 --> 22:23.461
I wonder if he eats spicy food.

22:23.961 --> 22:26.771
I also made
deep-fried potato shrimp for him.

22:27.311 --> 22:28.880
Zhangru, why are you...

22:28.881 --> 22:30.400
Su, what have you been doing over there

22:30.401 --> 22:31.541
all day?

22:33.031 --> 22:34.270
I made a sweet dish

22:34.271 --> 22:35.571
for good luck,

22:35.881 --> 22:37.771
called Hidden Treasures.

22:39.471 --> 22:40.741
It looks good.

22:40.921 --> 22:42.880
I don't know what Ji is thinking.

22:42.881 --> 22:45.011
The capital has many tasty food and fun.

22:45.011 --> 22:46.640
Why would he choose to live
in this remote manor?

22:46.641 --> 22:47.901
By the way,

22:48.071 --> 22:50.181
how did you two know each other?

22:51.311 --> 22:54.571
I first met him
when I was still a child.

22:54.881 --> 22:56.021
We met at Wanfo Temple.

22:57.971 --> 22:59.501
Your health is in such poor condition.

22:59.791 --> 23:02.811
You might as well go to heaven
instead of coming back to the village.

23:04.981 --> 23:06.270
(Records of the Enlightened Age)
Leave now.

23:06.271 --> 23:09.371
Misfortune can lead to something good
and they are connected.

23:09.791 --> 23:12.160
We're counting on both of you
to change the secret of heaven.

23:13.711 --> 23:15.790
Ji looks like a celestial being

23:15.791 --> 23:17.680
It's a waste for him to be a monk.

23:17.681 --> 23:19.941
I wonder if he's open
about being a matrilocal husband.

23:20.991 --> 23:21.990
Zhao,

23:21.991 --> 23:23.550
how far have you two progressed?

23:23.551 --> 23:25.901
I haven't seen him in ages.

23:25.901 --> 23:27.360
Then why are you still making
Peony fillet for him?

23:27.361 --> 23:28.270
I've never even tried it before.

23:28.271 --> 23:30.291
- Me too.
- I'll make it for you next time.

23:30.471 --> 23:31.400
Fourth Young Lady,

23:31.401 --> 23:33.421
Old Madam's migraines
are acting up again.

23:36.401 --> 23:37.270
Mister,

23:37.271 --> 23:38.771
how's Grandmother now?

23:39.451 --> 23:41.230
Her migraine has built up over time
because of emotional stress.

23:41.231 --> 23:42.090
It can't be rushed.

23:42.091 --> 23:43.400
Just follow the remedy I gave

23:43.401 --> 23:44.771
and recuperate slowly.

23:45.311 --> 23:47.141
- Thank you, mister.
- I shall make a move now.

23:49.791 --> 23:50.931
You're a quack!

23:51.791 --> 23:53.510
- Who are you calling a quack?
- The one who answers.

23:53.511 --> 23:55.710
- You...
- You're a quack, quack, quack.

23:55.711 --> 23:57.640
I won't argue
with a young brat like you.

23:57.641 --> 23:58.781
I'm leaving!

24:22.711 --> 24:23.570
If you follow

24:23.571 --> 24:25.230
that quack advice to treat her,

24:25.231 --> 24:26.371
even a god couldn't save her.

24:26.991 --> 24:28.221
Don't talk about bad luck.

24:28.401 --> 24:29.510
What?

24:29.511 --> 24:30.851
Will kind words heal her?

24:35.071 --> 24:36.701
Take off her clothes.

24:40.751 --> 24:42.051
You can save her, right?

24:43.171 --> 24:44.841
The root of the illness
is blocked energy.

24:44.841 --> 24:46.531
It's stuck at certain pressure points.

24:46.791 --> 24:48.781
One is above the navel,
and the other is on the foot.

24:48.791 --> 24:50.841
You'll need to remove her clothes
and use acupuncture.

24:50.841 --> 24:51.920
Since she's a woman,

24:51.921 --> 24:54.030
maybe we should find a female physician?

24:54.031 --> 24:55.501
But female physicians are rare.

24:56.551 --> 24:58.421
Grandmother won't eat or drink.

24:58.691 --> 24:59.981
We cannot afford to wait anymore.

25:04.991 --> 25:06.131
Grandmother.

25:06.161 --> 25:07.901
Everyone has their fate.

25:09.171 --> 25:11.571
Perhaps my time is ending.

25:12.401 --> 25:13.771
I just don't understand.

25:14.071 --> 25:16.291
It's a treatable illness,
but she refuses to be treated.

25:16.291 --> 25:17.440
If everything is
about rules and propriety,

25:17.441 --> 25:19.091
what do we need physicians for?

25:19.161 --> 25:20.270
Old Madam,

25:20.271 --> 25:21.501
isn't your life

25:21.511 --> 25:23.371
more important than those useless rules?

25:25.071 --> 25:26.160
Grandmother,

25:26.161 --> 25:28.531
a physician
doesn't discriminate genders.

25:28.591 --> 25:29.931
Everyone is patient in their eyes.

25:30.751 --> 25:34.141
I don't want to lose a loved one
because of these traditions.

25:34.531 --> 25:36.091
Please,

25:36.391 --> 25:37.611
just try it for me.

25:38.501 --> 25:39.891
Please, Grandmother.

25:47.601 --> 25:48.741
Ms. Longevity!

25:49.551 --> 25:50.691
Ms. Longevity!

25:51.441 --> 25:52.990
Grandmother finally took the medicine.

25:52.991 --> 25:54.550
I'll go and get her some plain congee.

25:54.551 --> 25:55.400
All right.

25:55.401 --> 25:57.120
Avoid meat and inflammatory foods
for the next few days.

25:57.121 --> 25:58.261
All right.

25:59.751 --> 26:00.891
Thank you very much.

26:01.441 --> 26:02.581
It's a small matter.

26:13.991 --> 26:15.181
Thank you.

26:15.961 --> 26:17.421
Grandmother finally fell asleep.

26:17.881 --> 26:20.371
Just because she's stable now
doesn't mean it'll last.

26:20.601 --> 26:22.221
Her health is affected

26:22.271 --> 26:24.031
by all the worries
she's been holding inside.

26:24.031 --> 26:26.221
If the root cause isn't addressed,
she won't live long.

26:29.551 --> 26:32.811
Grandmother has a heavy burden
in her heart.

26:33.971 --> 26:35.331
She doesn't want to talk about it.

26:35.791 --> 26:37.421
So I don't know how to help.

26:37.841 --> 26:40.160
If she doesn't want to resolve it,
that's her choice.

26:40.161 --> 26:41.741
Everyone has to face death eventually.

26:41.741 --> 26:43.291
Just stay by her side and support her.

26:45.881 --> 26:47.261
Did you glare at me

26:47.271 --> 26:48.680
because you think I'm heartless

26:48.681 --> 26:49.851
and cruel?

26:51.671 --> 26:53.131
I just don't understand

26:53.161 --> 26:55.741
why you treat life and death so lightly.

27:01.411 --> 27:03.461
My father said I was born
without the ability to feel,

27:03.601 --> 27:04.710
that I have little emotion.

27:04.711 --> 27:07.611
I've never shed a single tear
since I was a child.

27:07.841 --> 27:10.261
When I was four, he fell seriously ill.

27:10.991 --> 27:12.771
So he gave me this telescope.

27:12.921 --> 27:15.701
He said he would become a star.

27:15.751 --> 27:17.571
So I would gaze at the stars
every night,

27:17.881 --> 27:19.851
memorizing astronomy
and the calendar system.

27:20.751 --> 27:22.011
But deep down,

27:23.161 --> 27:24.301
I knew I would never find him

27:25.201 --> 27:28.531
because a person will turn to dust
when they die.

27:28.641 --> 27:29.781
Everyone dies.

27:30.881 --> 27:32.291
Life leads to death,

27:32.621 --> 27:34.421
and death marks the beginning
of life's cycle.

27:34.601 --> 27:35.741
That's right.

27:36.681 --> 27:38.501
What matters is how we live.

27:39.201 --> 27:42.491
Little Zhuang Zhou,
how do you want to live your life?

27:46.231 --> 27:47.741
I didn't think too much of it.

27:48.881 --> 27:50.181
To live a full life

27:50.511 --> 27:52.371
is rare enough.

27:53.881 --> 27:55.531
(It's a luxury)

27:57.601 --> 27:59.291
(for a person to live it well.)

28:00.361 --> 28:03.371
If you still have the strength,
help those around you.

28:03.921 --> 28:05.061
That would be enough.

28:05.441 --> 28:07.291
Are you content with such a small wish?

28:09.201 --> 28:11.501
So, have you decided not
to become a Buddhist monk?

28:11.921 --> 28:14.771
I was sent to the temple
because I was weak when I was young.

28:15.071 --> 28:16.941
There, I learned medicine
from the head monk.

28:16.941 --> 28:18.270
A small physician heals
the body from illness.

28:18.271 --> 28:19.701
A great physician heals the nation.

28:19.751 --> 28:21.421
It would be interesting
to hold the position

28:21.551 --> 28:22.771
of the Grand Secretary.

28:23.641 --> 28:24.790
I've looked into the history

28:24.791 --> 28:26.511
of the Grand Secretary
over the past three hundred years.

28:26.511 --> 28:28.400
It takes decades of promotion
and hard work.

28:28.401 --> 28:31.270
It'll take at least fifty years
to reach the second rank.

28:31.271 --> 28:32.200
That takes too long.

28:32.201 --> 28:33.160
So it's not worth it.

28:33.161 --> 28:34.421
I need to find another way.

28:35.921 --> 28:38.261
There's no shortcut
to becoming the Grand Secretary.

28:38.641 --> 28:41.941
Unless you become a dishonest
or a traitorous official.

28:42.161 --> 28:43.371
That could work, too.

28:45.991 --> 28:47.741
It's more interesting talking to you.

28:47.761 --> 28:50.060
When I return to the capital
after taking the imperial exam,

28:50.071 --> 28:51.211
we can discuss it further.

28:53.841 --> 28:57.501
Before you go to the capital,
I have one request.

28:59.441 --> 29:01.221
I want to learn medicine from you.

29:02.711 --> 29:06.461
Even though people
will always have to part,

29:06.921 --> 29:08.470
I want to make

29:08.471 --> 29:10.421
our time together last
as long as possible.

29:14.781 --> 29:19.281
(Official Record of Medicine)

29:32.311 --> 29:33.451
Not bad.

29:33.751 --> 29:35.600
Ji and Ms. Longevity meet secretly
every day.

29:35.601 --> 29:36.510
So they must have feelings
for each other now.

29:36.511 --> 29:37.651
Do you want to bet on it?

29:37.791 --> 29:39.291
Bring it on.

29:42.471 --> 29:43.990
A chicken and a duck.

29:43.991 --> 29:45.291
Such a perfect match.

29:48.991 --> 29:50.131
Let's begin.

29:56.271 --> 29:57.901
You did well dissecting
the chicken today.

29:58.401 --> 30:00.261
But we should try it on a human body.

30:00.271 --> 30:02.291
Let's go to the mass grave tonight.

30:02.311 --> 30:03.400
All right.

30:03.401 --> 30:05.771
How do you date at a mass grave?

30:06.881 --> 30:08.021
I lost.

30:17.681 --> 30:19.701
Ji Yong! Ji Yong, get up.

30:20.511 --> 30:22.531
Ji Yong. Ji Yong.

30:24.881 --> 30:27.371
Originally, I brought Ji Jianming
to the manor

30:27.751 --> 30:30.501
as a potential prospect
for Ms. Longevity.

30:30.791 --> 30:32.400
You're really wise.

30:32.401 --> 30:34.611
They look perfectly matched.

30:35.401 --> 30:37.470
One lacks emotion
and the other one is indifferent.

30:37.471 --> 30:38.981
It's indeed a good match.

30:41.281 --> 30:43.461
But too bad,
they have no feelings for each other

30:43.841 --> 30:45.871
and are not fated to be together.

30:46.461 --> 30:48.011
Remember to review the medical classics.

30:48.011 --> 30:49.880
If you fall behind in your progress
when I return,

30:49.881 --> 30:51.021
you will be punished with acupuncture.

30:51.201 --> 30:52.341
All right.

30:52.361 --> 30:54.801
But if you fail the exam,
you'll also get the same punishment.

30:55.441 --> 30:57.741
But it's too easy not to fail the exam.

30:57.791 --> 31:00.181
If I don't top the exam,
you can prick me however you want.

31:03.921 --> 31:05.371
As for the nation's illness,

31:05.371 --> 31:07.001
I've already checked the pulse
and made the diagnosis.

31:08.071 --> 31:11.571
I've heard the higher the position,
the harder it is to retire.

31:13.161 --> 31:16.120
Becoming a famous official
isn't necessarily interesting.

31:16.121 --> 31:17.680
Corrupt officials are just a symptom.

31:17.681 --> 31:19.811
The real problem lies in the system.

31:19.841 --> 31:22.230
If we clean it up from the top down,

31:22.231 --> 31:23.510
we could save a fortune.

31:23.511 --> 31:25.741
Then the country's landscape
could be transformed.

31:26.161 --> 31:27.301
Time for me to go now.

31:33.031 --> 31:36.051
(He's talented and ambitious.)

31:36.401 --> 31:37.960
(But why did he become a monk)

31:37.961 --> 31:39.771
(in the dream?)

31:40.361 --> 31:41.851
Oh, merciful Buddha.

31:43.231 --> 31:44.320
(Ji Yong, Prodigious Monk)
(The scholar respects)

31:44.321 --> 31:45.341
(Ji Yong, Prodigious Monk)
(the younger generation.)

31:45.411 --> 31:47.751
(Who dares to challenge Confucius
in counting the stars?)

31:48.551 --> 31:51.091
(Deal loyalty, treachery, gratitude,
and resentment lightly with a smile.)

31:51.751 --> 31:55.221
(A perfect harmony
between nature and spirit.)

31:59.221 --> 32:03.280
(Futing)

32:03.281 --> 32:04.791
Patience, everyone will have some.

32:07.811 --> 32:08.760
Bring more congee.

32:08.761 --> 32:10.161
We can't keep up already. Hurry up.

32:22.031 --> 32:27.840
♪The Grand Tutor tells me
the cause and reason♪

32:27.841 --> 32:31.221
Duke of Ding is in Futing helping
with the disaster relief.

32:31.401 --> 32:33.421
The government has run out of grain.

32:33.961 --> 32:37.571
We shouldn't go out drinking these days.

32:38.121 --> 32:39.421
What's there to be scared of?

32:40.071 --> 32:43.421
No, Song Mo is like
a living King of Hell.

32:43.641 --> 32:46.230
I've heard once he targets
someone for questioning,

32:46.231 --> 32:47.920
- Did you take the money?
- (he always finds the evidence.)

32:47.921 --> 32:49.120
No... No, I did not.

32:49.121 --> 32:51.941
Whether they're royals, rich merchants,
or high-ranking officials,

32:52.121 --> 32:53.611
he investigates them all.

32:58.401 --> 33:00.510
Song Mo, how dare you raid the Tang Family.

33:00.511 --> 33:02.181
Do you know who's my older brother?

33:03.551 --> 33:05.421
Do... Do you know who I am?

33:05.421 --> 33:07.750
The eight magnates
of the Tang Family dominate the salt trade,

33:07.751 --> 33:09.221
mining, and water transport in Futing.

33:09.311 --> 33:10.360
The entire Tang Family

33:10.361 --> 33:11.741
won't let you off!

33:21.921 --> 33:23.091
Who else?

33:29.921 --> 33:30.880
How dare you!

33:30.881 --> 33:32.360
Focus on your performance.

33:32.361 --> 33:34.180
How dare a mere performer
like you step on a guest's table?

33:34.181 --> 33:36.001
(Ding)

33:36.471 --> 33:37.611
Ding Army?

33:45.161 --> 33:46.301
General Song.

33:51.441 --> 33:52.840
- General Song.
- General Song.

33:52.841 --> 33:53.920
General Song, spare us.

33:53.921 --> 33:54.840
General Song, have mercy.

33:54.841 --> 33:56.310
I'll share half of the money with you.

33:56.311 --> 33:57.470
Please let me go.

33:57.471 --> 33:58.611
Sure.

33:59.071 --> 34:02.531
I'll let you keep half
of your limbs and organs.

34:05.401 --> 34:06.470
General, please check.

34:06.471 --> 34:08.701
All the funds we embezzled are here.

34:11.471 --> 34:13.221
This is enough
to keep your corpse whole.

34:15.111 --> 34:16.771
If you do not wish to die,

34:16.881 --> 34:20.621
tell me where you store
the grain reserves.

34:26.721 --> 34:28.411
Duke of Ding, please reconsider carefully.

34:28.631 --> 34:31.931
The emperor decreed
the crown prince to manage the relief.

34:32.111 --> 34:33.550
While your intentions are good,

34:33.551 --> 34:35.331
I cannot say anything

34:35.441 --> 34:38.221
against the emperor's decree.

34:38.241 --> 34:39.381
Eunuch Ding,

34:41.031 --> 34:44.331
tens of thousands
of people are in danger.

34:44.631 --> 34:45.800
We can't wait

34:45.801 --> 34:49.061
for the royal family to come
from miles away to put up a show.

34:49.511 --> 34:51.931
Do they know how many people die
from hunger every day?

34:52.761 --> 34:56.701
I've already opened the treasury
and started the relief myself.

34:57.551 --> 34:59.371
- Duke!
- Reply according to my words!

35:00.041 --> 35:02.141
I will take the responsibility
if anything happens.

35:03.631 --> 35:04.771
Marshal!

35:05.471 --> 35:07.030
Deputy Marshal Song bought grain
from a neighboring county

35:07.031 --> 35:08.440
with the confiscated bribe money

35:08.441 --> 35:09.931
and sent it to the congee stall.

35:13.111 --> 35:14.291
Well done, lad.

35:14.301 --> 35:15.800
(Twilight in Spring)

35:15.801 --> 35:16.810
I need to go and take a look.

35:16.811 --> 35:17.660
Old Madam.

35:17.661 --> 35:19.590
- Let me check it out. I'll be fine.
- You can't, Old Madam.

35:19.591 --> 35:21.030
- It's pouring heavily. You can't go.
- The rain is so heavy.

35:21.031 --> 35:22.171
Grandmother.

35:22.181 --> 35:24.030
- Ms. Longevity.
- You're just starting to recover.

35:24.031 --> 35:25.140
You can't be out in the rain.

35:25.141 --> 35:26.800
- Quickly.
- I'm too restless to stay put.

35:26.801 --> 35:28.510
It's raining so hard.

35:28.511 --> 35:30.150
We've prepared the grain.

35:30.151 --> 35:32.670
- We've fixed the foundation and roof.
- Hurry! Keep up!

35:32.671 --> 35:35.360
But how can the structure withstand
such heavy rain?

35:35.361 --> 35:38.510
These simple thatched houses
will definitely collapse.

35:38.511 --> 35:40.920
Those tenants will be left homeless
without food.

35:40.921 --> 35:42.411
Grandmother, don't worry.

35:42.571 --> 35:44.320
- I'm preparing to repair the canal
- Hurry.

35:44.321 --> 35:46.111
with the tenants and craftsmen
and send out the grain.

35:46.111 --> 35:48.141
We'll make sure
the villagers are all right.

35:48.361 --> 35:51.371
So stay here and distribute
the grains without worries.

35:51.371 --> 35:53.760
Ms. Tuo, keep Grandmother company
and give the instructions together

35:53.761 --> 35:55.110
and I'll take care of the rest.

35:55.111 --> 35:57.440
- But...
- Fourth Young Lady, don't worry.

35:57.441 --> 35:59.920
Ms. Longevity, you must be careful.

35:59.921 --> 36:01.411
I'll be careful so don't worry.

36:03.511 --> 36:04.971
Remember to be careful.

36:07.051 --> 36:08.150
Wait your turn, no pushing.

36:08.151 --> 36:09.630
No pushing! Back up!

36:09.631 --> 36:11.101
- Line up!
- There's enough for everyone!

36:11.181 --> 36:12.150
(Corruption and Abuse of Power)

36:12.151 --> 36:13.070
Take turns! One at a time!

36:13.071 --> 36:14.211
Don't drop it.

36:14.671 --> 36:16.221
Next one.

36:16.631 --> 36:18.510
Don't push. Everyone will have some.

36:18.511 --> 36:19.400
One at a time!

36:19.401 --> 36:21.581
I was here first. Give it to me!

36:23.191 --> 36:24.331
Mister,

36:24.921 --> 36:28.880
why is this hairpin made of white stone?

36:28.881 --> 36:32.331
Doesn't it feel heavy
with the stone on his head?

36:35.961 --> 36:37.101
Look.

36:40.111 --> 36:41.691
It's no longer heavy
once we take it off.

36:41.921 --> 36:43.280
No matter what it is made,

36:43.281 --> 36:44.800
you can exchange this
for 30 jin of rice.

36:44.801 --> 36:47.101
Then you and your parents
won't go hungry anymore.

36:47.551 --> 36:48.691
Take it.

36:49.631 --> 36:51.021
Thank you, mister.

36:53.321 --> 36:54.630
The grain cart is here!

36:54.631 --> 36:56.400
- The grain cart is here!
- The grain cart is here!

36:56.401 --> 36:57.400
Be careful!

36:57.401 --> 36:58.931
- Hurry!
- Watch it!

37:14.111 --> 37:15.251
Watch out!

37:26.551 --> 37:28.141
- Young Lady.
- Are you all right, Young Lady?

37:34.631 --> 37:35.920
- Sir!
- Mister!

37:35.921 --> 37:37.931
- Deputy Marshal!
- Sir! Sir!

37:38.151 --> 37:40.931
- Sir!
- Sir! Sir!

37:41.151 --> 37:42.811
- Sir! Sir!
- Mister!

38:00.441 --> 38:01.581
Who are you?

38:03.031 --> 38:05.101
Why are you here?

38:09.631 --> 38:10.931
How come it's you?

38:16.441 --> 38:17.931
We haven't met.

38:18.841 --> 38:20.061
So you cannot die.

38:43.441 --> 38:44.581
He's awake.

38:44.591 --> 38:45.630
- He's finally awake.
- He's up.

38:45.631 --> 38:46.760
He's up.

38:46.761 --> 38:47.931
Luckily, you've awaken.

38:48.321 --> 38:49.621
I'll let Marshal know.

38:51.921 --> 38:52.990
Sir.

38:52.991 --> 38:56.661
Three days ago, you suffered
a head injury from a hard object.

38:57.071 --> 38:59.510
We've tried medicine,
herbal concoction, and acupuncture.

38:59.511 --> 39:00.811
But you wouldn't wake up.

39:01.031 --> 39:04.291
Fortunately,
the Marshal saw this item and lit it.

39:04.401 --> 39:06.411
It had miraculous effects.

39:24.551 --> 39:26.510
Sir, what kind of fragrance is this?

39:26.511 --> 39:27.701
Benzoin.

39:28.071 --> 39:31.741
They say Emperor Xuanzong couldn't sleep
after Imperial Consort Yang's demise.

39:31.741 --> 39:32.880
His mind was in a state of confusion

39:32.881 --> 39:34.781
and he could only fall asleep
with this fragrance

39:34.841 --> 39:36.141
so he could dream of her.

39:37.281 --> 39:38.320
Oh, I get it now.

39:38.321 --> 39:39.880
Deputy Marshal dreamt of his sweetheart.

39:39.881 --> 39:41.181
Can you keep quiet?

39:44.921 --> 39:46.621
She saved my life.

39:49.671 --> 39:50.811
Where's Marshal?

39:50.991 --> 39:53.331
Marshal stayed by your bed
the whole night.

39:53.361 --> 39:54.240
Before dawn,

39:54.241 --> 39:56.371
he left to inspect
the newly repaired dikes.

39:57.441 --> 39:59.240
The weather this year is truly strange.

39:59.241 --> 40:00.630
Many places have been hit
by heavy rains.

40:00.631 --> 40:03.741
Even the Tianjin sentry
and Zhending suffered too.

40:06.031 --> 40:07.451
(Zhending.)

40:11.661 --> 40:12.911
Here, it's not that hot anymore.

40:13.581 --> 40:14.840
There are more if you still want some.

40:14.841 --> 40:16.541
Have a bite.

40:18.731 --> 40:19.630
Mother.

40:19.631 --> 40:20.720
- Here you go.
- Thank you very much.

40:20.721 --> 40:22.541
- Mother.
- Eat slowly.

40:25.031 --> 40:26.070
Have a bun.

40:26.071 --> 40:27.771
Thank you, Miss.

40:30.631 --> 40:31.550
Thank you.

40:31.551 --> 40:32.971
- Eat it.
- Thank you.

40:32.991 --> 40:34.701
Eat this bun.

40:35.031 --> 40:36.070
Take it.

40:36.071 --> 40:37.211
Thank you.

40:38.511 --> 40:39.651
How are you feeling now?

40:44.721 --> 40:45.861
Here you go.

40:46.961 --> 40:48.190
- Distribute these to them.
- All right.

40:48.191 --> 40:49.331
Thank you.

40:55.671 --> 40:56.811
Thank you.

40:56.991 --> 40:58.371
You'll be all right so don't worry.

41:27.901 --> 41:31.441
(Half a Month Later)

41:41.161 --> 41:42.761
I apologize for disturbing you so late.

41:42.841 --> 41:45.491
My surname is Mei
and a merchant from the south.

41:45.491 --> 41:48.160
We're passing through this area
and need a place to stay for the night.

42:02.151 --> 42:03.291
Young Lady, you're up.

42:04.191 --> 42:05.491
What's the hour now?

42:05.871 --> 42:07.541
Just past three-quarters
after the Yin hour.

42:10.551 --> 42:11.691
Young Lady,

42:12.071 --> 42:14.371
a group of merchants arrived
at the manor.

42:14.471 --> 42:16.291
The leader calls himself, Mr. Mei.

42:16.511 --> 42:18.990
But I noticed everyone
in the group walks quietly,

42:18.991 --> 42:20.331
with calloused palms.

42:20.631 --> 42:22.510
Mr. Chen has sent people here
multiple times,

42:22.511 --> 42:23.771
asking if you've woken up.

42:25.991 --> 42:27.541
Bring Mr. Chen here.

42:43.471 --> 42:44.760
They have surrounded the manor

42:44.761 --> 42:46.141
and planned to wipe us out.

42:46.161 --> 42:48.630
A hostage is your way to make a deal
that satisfies both sides.

42:48.631 --> 42:50.280
Whether it will be a massacre
or making a deal,

42:50.281 --> 42:51.590
is up to you to decide.

42:51.591 --> 42:53.721
Fourth Young Lady,
you've been living far from the court.

42:53.721 --> 42:56.581
How would you know so much
about the Duke of Ding case?

42:57.151 --> 42:59.221
Who exactly are you?

43:02.401 --> 43:06.021
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

43:06.241 --> 43:09.860
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

43:09.861 --> 43:15.601
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

43:16.211 --> 43:17.500
♪Where can
this restless heart find peace?♪

43:17.501 --> 43:20.640
♪Left alone in an empty hall♪

43:20.641 --> 43:24.461
♪A lifetime chasing fate's lonely call♪

43:24.521 --> 43:28.800
♪Watching seasons fade and storms rise♪

43:28.801 --> 43:31.380
♪It hurts but it's not all for nothing♪

43:31.381 --> 43:32.650
♪My heart is as empty as a quiet street♪

43:32.651 --> 43:35.620
♪Who cares about the path I walk alone?♪

43:35.621 --> 43:39.840
♪Would you take away
the weight of the past?♪

43:39.841 --> 43:41.770
♪Life is fleeting, like morning frost♪

43:41.771 --> 43:45.000
♪Even a moment feels endless with you♪

43:45.001 --> 43:51.321
♪Like a stream flowing steady
through time♪

43:53.101 --> 44:00.011
♪A lone flower falls from the eaves
with moonlight graces steps beneath♪

44:00.471 --> 44:07.761
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

44:08.031 --> 44:11.281
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

44:11.761 --> 44:15.471
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

44:15.491 --> 44:21.351
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

44:21.941 --> 44:23.220
♪In this chaotic world♪

44:23.221 --> 44:26.160
♪Only love lasts♪

44:26.161 --> 44:30.021
♪We'll get through
every challenge together♪

44:30.191 --> 44:34.420
♪No matter how cold
or uncertain the road♪

44:34.421 --> 44:37.000
♪There's nothing to fear
when I'm with you♪

44:37.001 --> 44:38.210
♪My heart feels empty♪

44:38.211 --> 44:41.180
♪But I can hear your voice♪

44:41.181 --> 44:45.400
♪In this life, under the moonlight
and across the oceans♪

44:45.401 --> 44:47.871
♪We'll find our way back to each other♪

44:47.901 --> 44:48.750
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

44:48.751 --> 44:49.650
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

44:49.651 --> 44:50.640
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)

44:50.641 --> 44:56.191
♪Together,
we'll make every moment count♪
